cillator)\",\"description\":\"This API returns the absolute price oscillator (APO) values. See also: mathematical reference.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The technical indicator of your choice. In this case, function=APO\"},\"enum\":[\"APO\"]},{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The name of the ticker of your choice. For example: symbol=IBM\"}},{\"name\":\"interval\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Time interval between two consecutive data points in the time series. The following values are supported: 1min, 5min, 15min, 30min, 60min, daily, weekly, monthly\"},\"enum\":[\"1min\",\"5min\",\"15min\",\"30min\",\"60min\",\"daily\",\"weekly\",\"monthly\"]},{\"name\":\"series_type\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The desired price type in the time series. Four types are supported: close, open, high, low\"},\"enum\":[\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\"]},{\"name\":\"month\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, this parameter is not set and the technical indicator values will be calculated based on the default length of the underlying intraday, daily, weekly, or monthly time series data. You can use the month parameter (in YYYY-MM format) to return technical indicators for a specific month in history. For example, month=2009-01.\"}},{\"name\":\"fastperiod\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Positive integers are accepted. By default, fastperiod=12.\"}},{\"name\":\"slowperiod\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Positive integers are accepted. By default, slowperiod=26.\"}},{\"name\":\"matype\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Moving average type. By default, matype=0. Integers 0 - 8 are accepted with the following mappings. 0 = Simple Moving Average (SMA), 1 = Exponential Moving Average (EMA), 2 = Weighted Moving Average (WMA), 3 = Double Exponential Moving Average (DEMA), 4 = Triple Exponential Moving Average (TEMA), 5 = Triangular Moving Average (TRIMA), 6 = T3 Moving Average, 7 = Kaufman Adaptive Moving Average (KAMA), 8 = MESA Adaptive Moving Average (MAMA).\"},\"enum\":[\"0\",\"1\",\"2\",\"3\",\"4\",\"5\",\"6\",\"7\",\"8\"]},{\"name\":\"datatype\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, datatype=json. Strings json and csv are accepted with the following specifications: json returns the daily time series in JSON format; csv returns the time series as a CSV (comma separated value) file.\"},\"enum\":[\"json\",\"csv\"]}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"IBM\",\"function\":\"APO\",\"interval\":\"daily\",\"series_type\":\"close\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":812.96,\"success_rate\":0.562}},{\"tool_id\":\"binance.ticker.24hr.retrieve.v1\",\"name\":\"Get 24h Price Change Statistics\",\"description\":\"Get 24hr ticker statistics for all symbols.; Use this endpoint to get price change data for the past 24hrs.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Parameter symbol and symbols cannot be used in combination. If neither parameter is sent, tickers for all symbols will be returned in an array\"}},{\"name\":\"symbols\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Exaples of accepted format for the symbols parameter: [\\\"BTCUSDT\\\", \\\"BNBUSDT\\\"] or %5B%22BTCUSDT%22, %22BNBUSDT%22%5D\"}},{\"name\":\"type\",\"type\":\"ENUM\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Supported values: `FULL` or `MINI`.If none provided,the default is `FULL`. `FULL` is the default value and the response that is currently being returned from the endpoint. `MINI` omits the following fields from the response: `priceChangePercent` , `weightedAvgPrice` ,`bidPrice` , `bidQty` , `askPrice` , `askQty` , and `lastQty`\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"type\":\"FULL\",\"symbol\":\"BTCUSDT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"The world s leading cryptocurrency exchange platform. Secure, low fees, trusted by millions of users worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":160.78,\"success_rate\":0.969}}],\"search_id\":\"8b6ed038-15ef-4d36-89f0-cc522381c46f\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":147.74}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772588054065}}
